title: Patriots, Bill Belichick, Dak Prescott, free agency, and the Herd Hierarchy
itunes:title: Patriots, Bill Belichick, Dak Prescott, free agency, and the Herd Hierarchy
description:
Colin explains the Patriots plan going forward, why Bill Belichick knows what he's doing, what Travis Frederick's retirement means for Dak Prescott, and his new Herd Hierarchy of free agency. Guests include Howie Long, Joel Klatt, Matt Mosley, and Danny Kanell.
